<b>OpenBSD 2.9$B$N>l9g(B</b>

<p>
OpenBSD 2.9$B$G$O!"(Bwsconsctl$B%3%^%s%I$N0z?t$,>/$70c$$$^$9!#(B
$BFC$K!"(B``keyboard''$B%-!<%o!<%I$rA0$KIU$1$kI,MW$,$"$j$^$;$s$,!"(B
$B%3%^%s%I$r%G%P%$%9$N%-!<%\!<%IItJ,$KE,MQ$9$k$3$H$r;XDj$9$k$?$a$K(B
``-k''$B%U%i%0$rIU$1$kE@@$,0[$J$j$^$9!#(B

<blockquote><pre>
# <strong>wsconsctl -k -w encoding=uk</strong>
</pre></blockquote>

<p>$B$b$&$R$H$D$NNc$G$O!"0J2<$NDL$j$G$9!#(B

<blockquote><pre>
# <strong>wsconsctl -k -w map+="keysym Caps_Lock = Control_L"</strong>
</pre></blockquote>

<p>
